+ * For the SPSR layout seen from AArch32, see:
+ * - ARM DDI 0406C.d, page B1-1148
+ * - ARM DDI 0487E.a, page G8-6264
+ *
+ * For the SPSR_ELx layout for AArch32 seen from AArch64, see:
+ * - ARM DDI 0487E.a, page C5-426
